      <title>特朗普和参议院共和党人未能解决美国债务上限问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/thune-says-debt-ceiling-solution-undecided-after-trump-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统和主要参议院共和党人在周四举行了白宫会议后，仍在寻求解决债务上限的解决方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/thune-says-debt-ceiling-solution-undecided-after-trump-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 22:05:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的加拿大大使提名人同意这是一个主权国家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/trump-s-nominee-for-ambassador-to-canada-tries-to-make-light-of-51st-state-jabs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）选择加拿大大使的选择证实了该国作为主权国家的地位，并暗示了总理与总理贾斯汀·特鲁多（Justin Trudeau）的复杂关系可能在他的呼吁中发挥了作用，将其吞并到美国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/trump-s-nominee-for-ambassador-to-canada-tries-to-make-light-of-51st-state-jabs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 21:49:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国，美国举行私人会谈，以使苹果加密仇恨平静下来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/uk-us-hold-private-talks-in-bid-to-calm-apple-encryption-feud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士说，英国官员已经与美国同行进行了私人会谈，以解决对英国试图迫使苹果公司的担忧，以便为美国人的加密数据建立后门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/uk-us-hold-private-talks-in-bid-to-calm-apple-encryption-feud</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 21:48:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
